<br>
We were puzzled but finally someone suggested he may have got charmed by Lord Fesh and became his pet. That would make sense why he con indiff. Also, we tried to pull him back to his pit.. lost aggro, he pathed back to Lord Fesh's cave!!<br>
<br>
