<br>
Vyemm was up, Aary, Ikatiar and Eashan were up.<br>
<br>
Other guilds were after Aary, Ikatiar and Eashan so we went after Vyemm first.<br>
<br>
When one of our monks caught aggro from Vyemm...Aary ran over and became his pet.<br>
We suspect all the Lords/Ladys can do the same.<br>
